items.headline: Stop guessing and wasting time! Follow our proven 5-step process taking you from idea all the way through to launch!
objectives_summary: Literally step by step how to launch your fashion brand online. This course will cover everything from idea validation to planning an ecommerce collection; considering hemisphere, climate, culture, sustainability + more, and then how to produce a 1st collection covering topics like how to source, how to find a manufacturer, how to create tech packs, how to fit your product + more and then onto how to be compliant and how to ship. Aside from the creatives, a fundamental part of the course is how to set up your business covering trademarks, domain names + more, through to how to set a sales plan, budget and manage your cash flow. The final 2 steps focus on building a brand - DTC build (website), marketing, branding, social media + more and actually how to launch! Then finally upon launch how to grow globally covering numerous methods that will last for at least the 1st 5 years of business!
How to project manage a business launch on ecommerce
How to source and how to find a manufacturer to produce your 1st collection
